{"id": "1369668198999527516", "channel_id": "1369668198999527516", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n       彌薩格大學校務處將於5月7日21:40進行校內設施修復，更新完成後您將得到通知，重新進入遊戲。對於更新可能給大家帶來的不便，我們會準備一份補給物資以示歉意。祝大家調查順利！ \n  \n【補給物資】\n在線維護補償：銀芯*50\n  \n【領取條件】\n領取時間截至2025年5月21日23:59。請記得及時前往郵箱領取補給物資哦。  \n \n【更新內容】\n一、喚醒體\n【克珀珊特】\n● 懲戒雷霆：新增「餘波：此卡回到抽牌堆頂部。」\n \n二、相位對弈\n● 海上領航者：回覆生命由 12 降低為 9。\n● 純銀的初心：現在裝備者自身死亡時不會觸發命輪效果。\n \n三、優化與問題修復\n● 優化了「承受觸腕傷害提高」效果狀態，現在能夠正確展示了。\n● 優化了造物「超維指輪」，現在會額外提供 1 造物上限。\n● 修復了「克珀珊特」喚醒體試玩活動中，玩家血量會因守密人等級而改變的問題。\n● 修復了喚醒體「珊」釋放超限爆發後，若手牌中有多張「珊」的「打擊」，部分打擊文本描述錯誤的問題。\n● 修復了喚醒體「血鏈·希洛」的技能「鮮血鏈條」存在「消耗」詞綴時，打出後不會回到手中的問題。\n● 修復了「維度影像 · 溫柯爾」未能隨其它喚醒體釋放狂氣爆發而獲得狂氣和算力消耗降低效果的問題。\n● 修復了「相位對弈」中「聖火中的指引」裝備後顯示卡圖錯誤的問題。\n● 修復了「相位對弈」中「海上領航者」裝備後實際效果錯誤的問題。\n● 優化了英語版的翻譯問題。\n● 修復了「異夢視界」中「褻瀆」劇情「血宴」存在劇情卡住的問題。\n● 修復了「校友捐獻基金」無法領取的問題。\n● 修復了戰鬥中拖動部分描述過長的手牌時、可能發生出牌卡住的問題。\n● 修復了「克珀珊特」活動子頁面在關閉時、左上角文本殘留的顯示效果問題。\n● 修復了「克珀珊特」活動商店角色立繪顯示效果不佳的問題。\n● 修復了喚醒體「圖魯」技能故事的錯別字。", "timestamp": "2025-05-07T13:32:25.846000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "⛵", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1369668199171231755", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131424, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1369668198999527516/1369668199171231755/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=69cc75a9&is=69cb2429&hm=c78b727d206c388a5e83967d902cc5d9ecbbc13b405274c7026871ecf99bd017&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1369668198999527516", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.1.3 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1369668704576737401", "channel_id": "1369668198999527516", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "Dear Keeper,\n    The Mythag University Administration Office will conduct facility repairs on May 7 at 21:40(UTC+8). You will be notified once the update is complete and can re-enter the game. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and will provide a supply package as compensation. Happy investigating!\n    \n【Supply Package】\nMaintenance Compensation: Silver*50\n    \n【Claim Conditions】\nClaim period ends on May 21 2025(UTC+8), at 23:59. Please remember to check your mailbox to claim the supply package.\n     \n【Update Content】\nI. Awaker\n【Corposant】\n● Thunder of Retribution: Added \"Aftershock: This card returns to the top of the draw pile.\"\n \nII. Traphase\n● Navigator of the Seas: Life recovery reduced from 12 to 9.\n● Pure Silver's Origin: No longer triggers Wheel of Destiny effect upon the wearer's death.\n \nIII. Optimization and Bug Fixes\n● Optimized the \"Increased Tentacle Damage Taken\" status effect, now displays correctly.\n● Optimized the relic \"Ultra Dimensional Ring,\" now provides an additional relic limit.\n● Fixed the issue where player health would change based on Keeper level during the Coppersant Awaker trial event.\n● Fixed the issue where Awaker \"Sanga\" had incorrect text descriptions for multiple \"Strike\" cards after using Over-Exaltation.\n● Fixed the issue with Awaker \"Helot-Catena\" skill \"Blood Chain\" not returning to hand when the \"Exhaust\" prefix is present.\n● Fixed the issue where \"Dimensional Image · Winkle\" did not gain reduced Aliemus and Arithmetica consumption when other Awakers triggered Exalt.\n● Fixed the incorrect card image display issue for \"Guidance in the Sacred Fire\" in Traphase.\n● Fixed the actual effect error for \"Navigator of the Seas\" in Traphase.\n● Optimized translation issues in the English version.\n● Fixed the storyline freeze issue in \"Dreamscape\" during the \"Desecration\" scene \"Bloody Feast.\"", "timestamp": "2025-05-07T13:34:26.385000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1369668198999527516", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.1.3 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1369668725783138324", "channel_id": "1369668198999527516", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "● Fixed the issue where \"Alumni Donation Fund\" could not be claimed.\n● Fixed the issue where dragging cards with overly long descriptions during battle could cause card play to freeze.\n● Fixed the residual text display issue in the top left corner when closing the Coppersant event subpage.\n● Fixed the poor display quality of character illustrations in the Coppersant event shop.\n● Fixed the typo in Awaker \"Tulu\" skill story.\n \nTranslation Optimization（EN Only）\n● Fixed an issue where Awakener Sanga's name was incorrectly displayed as \"Corposant\".\n● Added human proofread voiceline text for Awakener Corposant.\n● Added human proofread skill and story descriptions for the following Wheels of Destiny:\n\"Flamebound Navigator\",\"Navigator at Sea\".\n● Optimized UI text in the \"Assignments\", \"Curriculum\", \"Traphase\", \"Settings\", and \"Awakener Voicelines\" panels.\n● Fixed incorrect machine translations for:\nAwakener Corposant's Talent: \"Cinders\" (previously \"Remaining fire\")\nTraphase Skill: \"To Sail the Sundered Tides\" (previously \"Guiding Light of the Abyssal Sea\")\nRelic: \"Guidance of Erasmus\"\n● Fixed a mistranslation where \"Lemuria\" appeared as \"Luoyan\" in Awakener Sanga's Exalt voiceline text.\n● Fixed an issue where Tawil and N's Orison names were displayed incorrectly.\n● Fixed an issue where the Awakening Details text for \"Realm Study\" was displayed incorrectly.\n● Fixed miscellaneous spelling errors.\n● A known technical issue may cause certain English story text to display incorrectly with exposed html codes. We are working on addressing this issue.\n● A known technical issue may cause certain UI text in the \"Extra Curriculum\" panel to display incorrectly. We are working on addressing this issue.", "timestamp": "2025-05-07T13:34:31.441000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-07T13:34:37.455000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "⛵", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "💩", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1369668198999527516", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.1.3 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
